          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 157,
          "end": 166
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "老子曰師之所處荆棘生焉大軍之後必有凶年",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 34
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "詩曰雨我公田遂及我私孟子曰方里而井井九百畆其中為公田八家皆私百畆同養公田公事畢然後敢治私事所以别野人也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 80
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
